@startuml
title Offline Package Webpack Plugin - Control Flow

actor Developer
participant "Webpack Build\nProcess" as Webpack
participant "OfflinePackagePlugin" as Plugin
participant "JSZip Library" as JSZip
participant "mime-types\nLibrary" as MimeTypes
participant "File System" as FS
database "Build Assets" as Assets

Developer -> Webpack: Configure plugin in\nwebpack config
activate Webpack

Developer -> Webpack: Run webpack build
Webpack -> Webpack: Process application files
Webpack -> Webpack: Generate build assets

Webpack -> Plugin: Hook into 'emit' phase
activate Plugin

Plugin -> Plugin: Initialize with\nconfiguration options\n(fileTypes, excludeFileName)

Plugin -> Assets: Retrieve list of\ngenerated assets
activate Assets
Assets --> Plugin: Return asset list
deactivate Assets

Plugin -> Plugin: Filter assets based on\nfileTypes and excludeFileName

loop For each included asset
    Plugin -> Plugin: getFileType(filename)
    Plugin -> MimeTypes: Detect MIME type
    activate MimeTypes
    MimeTypes --> Plugin: Return MIME type
    deactivate MimeTypes

    Plugin -> Assets: Read asset content
    activate Assets
    Assets --> Plugin: Return file content
    deactivate Assets

    Plugin -> JSZip: Add file to zip archive
    activate JSZip
    JSZip --> Plugin: File added
    deactivate JSZip

    Plugin -> Plugin: Add entry to index.json\n(path, remote URL, version, MIME type)
end

Plugin -> Plugin: Generate index.json manifest
Plugin -> JSZip: Add index.json to zip
activate JSZip
JSZip --> Plugin: Manifest added
deactivate JSZip

Plugin -> JSZip: generateAsync() -\nCreate zip archive
activate JSZip
JSZip -> JSZip: Compress files
JSZip --> Plugin: Return zip buffer
deactivate JSZip

Plugin -> Webpack: Add offline package zip\nto webpack output
Plugin -> Webpack: Add index.json\nto webpack output

deactivate Plugin

Webpack -> FS: Write offline package\nand manifest to disk
activate FS
FS --> Webpack: Files written
deactivate FS

Webpack --> Developer: Build complete with\noffline package
deactivate Webpack

@enduml
